Class SQLXMLImpl.SAXResultAdapter

java.lang.Object
org.xml.sax.helpers.XMLFilterImpl
org.postgresql.pljava.jdbc.SQLXMLImpl.SAXResultAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
TransformerHandler, ContentHandler, DTDHandler, EntityResolver, ErrorHandler, LexicalHandler, XMLFilter, XMLReader
Enclosing class:
SQLXMLImpl<V extends Datum>
static class SQLXMLImpl.SAXResultAdapter extends XMLFilterImpl implements TransformerHandler
Class to wrap a SAX TransformerHandler and hook the endDocument callback to also close the underlying output stream, making the SQLXML object ready to use for storing or returning the value.
